songs.title: Gabru
songs.lyrics:
Mundri banai phire te vich nagaj divayi phire
Mundri banai phire te vich nagaj divayi phire
Ik pase billo tera naa likhwaai phire
Pyar tenu karda ae gabru, pyaar bada karda ae gabru
Sare aakhde tu latni di agg di te pucchan ton darda ae gabru
Pyar tenu karda ae gabru
Saare aakhde tu laatni di agg di te pucchan ton darda ae gabru

Sanga 'ch lako lainda dil wali gal ni, saara din betha rehnda raah teri mal ni
Saara din baitha rehnda raah teri mal ni, saara din baitha rehnda raah teri mal ni
Sanga 'ch lako lainda dil wali gal ni, saara din betha rehnda raah teri mal ni
Baah vich sadh da ae gabru, ni oh pal tharda ae gabru
Saare aakhde tu laatni di agg di te pucchan ton darda ae gabru
Pyaar tenu karde gabru
Saare aakhde tu laatni di agg di te pucchan ton darde gabru

Teri eid vich billo lag gayian akkhiyan
Bandh darwaje vich rehndiyan na dakiyan
Teri eid vich billo lag gayian akkhiyan
Bandh darwaje vich rehndiyan na dakiyan
Jaanda vekh marde gabru, ni raahi dil karde gabru
Sare aakhde tu laatni di agg di te pucchan ton darde gabru
Pyaar tenu karde gabru
Saare aakhde tu laatni di agg di te pucchan ton darde gabru

Chup chup rahe kujh sakda na bol nai
Jhalla hoya phirda ae Inder Deol ni
Chup chup rahe kujh sakda na bol nai, jhalla hoya phirda ae Inder Deol ni

Sochan vich hadh da ae gabru, ho bimbo de na tarr de gabru
Saare aakhde tu laatni di agg di te pucchan ton darrde gabru
Pyaar tenu karde gabru
Saare aakhde tu laatni di agg di te pucchan ton darde gabru
Pyaar tenu karde gabru...
